grph.oo

Class ObjectGrph<V,E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • grph.oo.ObjectGrph<V,E>
  • Type Parameters:
    V -
    E - 

    public class ObjectGrph<V,E>
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides an object-oriented interface to the functionality provided by the Grph library. This is particularly useful when Grph is to be integrated to software projects that implies graph of objects.
